title: 202: College Football Recap, NFL Rookies
itunes:title: 202: College Football Recap, NFL Rookies
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks recap a wild opening weekend in college football including UCLA's comeback win over Texas A&M and Alabama's victory over Florida State. The guys also break down what they saw from notable NFL rookies in the preseason.
